00:44:39,639 --> 00:44:40,980
Nemůžu tomu uvěřit.

655
00:44:41,480 --> 00:44:43,379
- Stojíte mi na knížce! 
- Cože?

656
00:44:45,210 --> 00:44:46,210
Promiň.

657
00:44:46,210 --> 00:44:47,850
Kde se tam vzala?

658
00:44:47,850 --> 00:44:49,220
